#STEPS TO CREATE NEW PROJECT:

1. Open VSCode

2. Ctrl + Shift + P

3. Type:
   Spring Initializr: Create a Maven Project

4. Select:
   Version  → 3.5.14
   Language → Java
   Group    → com.dell
   Artifact → demo
   Package  → Jar
   Java     → 17

5. Dependencies:
   → Spring Web
   → Lombok

6. Select folder to save

7. Open in VSCode!
